of that issue.</font>
<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Q:</b></font><font face="Times New Roman"> Was one of the materials that you had received in our packet
an indication that Attorneys General in other states had indicated some
considerable doubts about the constitutionality of the bill?</font>
<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>A:</b></font><font face="Times New Roman"> Probably I did, but that's not unusual. I think everybody,
when they want to try to defeat a bill on the floor of the Senate, will
