it's
<br>&nbsp;</font><P>&nbsp;<P><font face="Times New Roman">392</font>
<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>A:</b></font><font face="Times New Roman"> (Continuing) unconstitutional or not is through this process;
not any other way.</font>
<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Q:</b></font><font face="Times New Roman"> Do you recall that there was a letter from a number of creation
science proponents to the Attorney General of South Carolina questioning
the Attorney General's opinion which said that the bill was unconstitutional?</font>
<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>A:</b></font><font face="Times New Roman"> I may have had one. I didn't think that was very relevant.
