<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>Q:</b></font><font face="Times New Roman"> I want to ask you about balance and what balance means to you?</font>
<p><font face="Times New Roman"><b>A:</b></font><font face="Times New Roman"> Balance to me means equal emphasis. I don't think you measure
